                        Are you sure you want to delete this Award Type?</h5>
                    <br />
                    <div class="form-group col-xs-12">
                        <div class="display-label">
                            <strong style="font-size: 1.2em; color: #F47C3C">@Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.Name)</strong>
